     * Converts a UInt8 number to the corresponding RenderingMode.
     * 0 -> Default, 1 -> Aliased, 2 -> GdiClassic, 3 -> GdiNatural,
     * 4 -> Natural, 5 -> NaturalSymmetric, any other value -> Outline
